data.description: Step into this beautifully updated home just beyond Topeka's city limits, where classic charm meets modern comfort. With 10' ceilings, wide white trim, and durable hardwood floors, this home was completely remodeled in 2017. The primary bedroom is a tranquil escape with its private bathroom, showcasing a tiled walk-in shower and a separate HVAC mini split unit. Each bedroom boasts walk-in closets, providing ample storage. The eat-in kitchen radiates style with under-cabinet lighting, a tile backsplash, white shaker-style cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient pantry. The main floor bathroom offers the choice of a clawfoot tub for relaxation or a pristine walk-in tile shower for convenience. Nestled on nearly 1.5 acres, the property encompasses a heated two-car garage, a carport, and a pet-friendly fenced yard. The back lot is home to a unique pallet deck featuring a covered bar, perfect for outdoor gatherings. Moreover, the expansive private land is a haven for hunting enthusiasts and wildlife lovers alike. Discover your dream home today!
